title: your account is in the process of transferring
body:
Yesterday i bhought RP for â‚¬30. Then i was going to transfer it back to EU West. I have transfered this account back to West before and nothing happend. But this time when im about to log in it says " your account is in the process of transferring ". I actually dont know how to fix it. I waited for 8 hours and nothing happend. But i can log in on my account back on east and have the same amount of RP left. 

PLEASE HELP!

replies.body: I went ahead and pulled up this account, and it looks like something went a little wrong with the transfer process. Reach out to our account team in a [**ticket**](https://support.riotgames.com/hc/en-us/requests/new) and they'll be able to get that transfer pushed through for you!
